@startuml
!pragma layout smetana

title Delete Bullet Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant Resumake
participant Parser
participant DeleteCommand
participant RecordList
participant Record
participant Storage

User -> Resumake: deletebullet 2 1
Resumake -> Parser: parse(input, ui)
Parser --> Resumake: DeleteCommand (bullet mode)
Resumake -> DeleteCommand: execute(list)
DeleteCommand -> RecordList: getRecord(1)
DeleteCommand -> Record: deleteBullet(0)
DeleteCommand --> Resumake: success
Resumake -> Storage: saveToFile(list)
Storage -> Storage: serialize + compare + write if changed
@enduml
